  searchable_text = $$Fall 2025: One-semester furniture pilot across 4 classrooms, complete. February 3, 2026: Theme Review, initial qualitative theme review with R&B team, complete. February 6, 2026: Insights Review, updated findings reviewed with Wendy and presented to Interiors group, complete. February 7, 2026: Midland Presentation, findings presented to Midland ISD, complete. May 2026: Sample Rodeo, broader stakeholder presentation to inform final furniture selections, pending.$$,
